  "local_port": 51068,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Where can I get beautiful collection for bridal dresses in Sydney?",
  "response": "Sydney is renowned for its exquisite bridal boutiques and collections. Here are some top places where you can find beautiful bridal dresses:\n\n### 1. **Rachel Gilbert Bridal**\n   - Known for its luxurious and modern designs, Rachel Gilbert offers a stunning collection of bridal gowns.\n   - **Location:** Shop 3, The Gowings Building, 45 Market Street, Sydney.\n\n### 2. **Mori Lee**\n   - Offers a wide range of bridal gowns from traditional to contemporary styles.\n   - **Location:** Showrooms are available in various bridal boutiques across Sydney.\n\n### 3. **Vera Wang Bridal**\n   - For a high-end, designer experience, Vera Wang\u2019s Sydney boutique offers her iconic bridal collections.\n   - **Location:** Level 1, 22 Albert Road, South Melbourne (but available through select retailers in Sydney).\n\n### 4. **J\u2019Aton Couture**\n   - Specializes in custom-made bridal gowns, perfect for brides seeking a unique and personalized design.\n   - **Location:** 10 Elizabeth Bay Road, Elizabeth Bay, Sydney.\n\n### 5. **Mariana Hardwick**\n   - Known for timeless and elegant designs, Mariana Hardwick\u2019s bridal collection is a favorite among brides.\n   - **Location:** 581 Sydney Road, Seaforth, Sydney.\n\n### 6. **The Bridal Atelier**\n   - Offers a curated selection of designer bridal gowns from both Australian and international designers.\n   - **Location:** 6/72 Wattle Street, Ultimo, Sydney.\n\n### 7. **Madi Lane Bridal**\n   - Features a range of romantic and feminine bridal gowns.\n   - **Location:** Available through various stockists in Sydney, including The Bridal Atelier.\n\n### 8. **Leah Da Gloria**\n   - Known for delicate lace and intricate beadwork, Leah Da Gloria offers luxurious bridal gowns.\n   - **Location:** Available through select bridal boutiques in Sydney.\n\n### 9. **Jillian Bride**\n   - Offers a selection of chic and stylish bridal gowns.\n   - **Location:** 128 Commonwealth St, Surry Hills, Sydney.\n\n### 10. **Anna Campbell**\n   - Specializes in bohemian-inspired bridal gowns with a vintage twist.\n   - **Location:** 32 Moncur Street, Woollahra, Sydney.\n\n### Tips for Bridal Shopping in Sydney:\n- **Book an Appointment:** Many bridal boutiques require appointments, so it\u2019s best to call ahead.\n- **Budget:** Have a clear budget in mind as bridal gowns can vary significantly in price.\n- **Timeline:** Start shopping at least 6-9 months before your wedding to allow time for fittings and alterations.\n\nThese boutiques and designers offer a variety of styles to suit different tastes and preferences, ensuring you\u2019ll find the perfect bridal dress for your special day.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
